              "duration": 2500
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "text": "Iblis hated the answer that Adam would represent.",
              "arabicText": "إبليس كان يكره الإجابة التي سيمثّلها آدم",
              "duration": 3000
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "text": "He hated that Adam's existence, standing firm and whole before God, meant that the case was lost.",
              "arabicText": "كان يكره أن وجود آدم صامداً معافىً شاهداً لله يعني أن القضية خُسرت",
              "duration": 4000
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "text": "So Iblis decided not to fight Adam...",
              "arabicText": "فقرّر إبليس ألا يُقاتل آدم",
              "duration": 2500
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "text": "But to transform him into evidence against himself.",
              "arabicText": "بل أن يحوّله إلى دليل اتهام ضد نفسه",
              "duration": 3000
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
